  "author_association": "MEMBER",
  "active_lock_reason": null,
  "body": "Nethermind validators need to be able to actively change the gas limit.\r\n\r\nIn Geth and Parity it is done via config.\r\nI believe it should be allowed to set it by miner_setTargetGasLimit in JSON RPC.\r\n\r\nThen this value should be passed further to the block producers.\r\n\r\nIConfig is not supporting any dynamic configurations which are supported via Options in .NET Core.\r\nIt may be too big a change to try to introduce options.\r\n\r\nInstead we can create a separate interface or just set the value on the IBlockProducer interface.",
